    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="How to Earn ATLAS in Star Atlas" class="article-title">
          How to Earn ATLAS in Star Atlas
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T18:23:33Z" title="2025-12-08T18:23:33Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 18:23</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47061460246163-How-to-Earn-ATLAS-in-Star-Atlas/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><a href="https://support.staratlas.com/star-atlas-tokens" rel="noopener"><strong>ATLAS</strong></a> is the main utility token of the Star Atlas economy. It can be used to buy NFTs (ships, crew, resources, skin and more) and reduce marketplace fees and most importantly, <strong>you can earn it directly by playing</strong>.</p><p>Here are the primary ways to earn ATLAS today:</p><h3 id="h_01KBJR4VH87HFFRH2ERW80D7FJ">Play-to-Earn in SAGE Labs (via Starbased)</h3><p><a href="https://based.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener">SAGE Labs</a> is a browser-based blockchain game where all player actions are on-chain. You’ll need a Solana wallet, a small amount of SOL, and some starting assets (ship, crew, and R4 resources).</p><p>Once you're in, you can earn ATLAS through the following methods:</p><h4 id="h_01KBJR4VH8JP48SH8X2VCP4HTK">1. Mine Resources and Sell Them</h4><p>Travel the Galia Expanse, extract raw materials, and sell them to other players through the Star Atlas Marketplace or directly on-chain.</p><h4 id="h_01KBJR4VH8788Q12QMXTT5X2ZG">2. Craft and Sell Components</h4><p>Use raw materials to <strong>craft items, </strong>like refined resources, components, or ship parts—and sell them for ATLAS.</p><h4 id="h_01KBJR4VH81DAB57P3E6TXZ13Z">3. Submit Resources to Starbase</h4><p>Deliver resources to help <strong>maintain and upgrade</strong> your faction’s Starbases.</p><ul>
<li><p>Contribute to <strong>upkeep</strong>: Keep the Starbase operational and functional for all players.</p></li>
<li><p>Help <strong>upgrade Starbase tiers</strong>: Your contributions support the faction’s progress and unlock faster crafting and other benefits.</p></li>
</ul><p>In return, you earn <strong>Loyalty Points (LP) </strong>that can be <strong>redeemed for ATLAS</strong></p><h4 id="h_01KBJR4VH8B35MV1R6K8C5R2SF">4. Craft and Sell FICs (Faction Infrastructure Contracts)</h4><p>Faction Infrastructure Contracts (FICs) are special items you can craft at any Starbase controlled by your faction. Once crafted, they can be sold back to the <strong>Council of Peace</strong> for a fixed reward of <strong>2 ATLAS per FIC</strong> through faction-specific buy orders at designated Starbases.</p><ul>
<li><p>Each faction has a unique recipe requiring components like Frameworks and Survey Data Units.</p></li>
<li><p>FIC buy orders rotate <strong>dynamically.</strong> A refill and rotation&nbsp; occurs <strong>only after both FIC buy orders for a faction have been fully depleted</strong>.</p></li>
<li><p>Sales are subject to the standard 6% Marketplace fee (reduced if you <a href="https://support.staratlas.com/how-does-the-atlas-locker-work" rel="noopener">lock ATLAS</a>).</p></li>
<li><p>This system complements LP rewards and provides a <strong>predictable, guaranteed income stream</strong> for crafters and haulers.</p></li>
</ul><h4 id="h_01KBJR4VH8QSXAXJ22KFFKKVRK">5. Rent Out Your Fleet</h4><p>You can list your SAGE fleet on the <strong>Fleet Rental platform</strong> (found on <a href="https://play.staratlas.com/rentals/" rel="noopener">play.staratlas.com</a>) and let other players rent your ships. This allows you to <strong>earn passive ATLAS</strong> from unused assets</p><h3 id="h_01KBJR4VH8PFJXYYMXQHQEXJ7V">What You’ll Need</h3><p>To start earning ATLAS in SAGE Labs:</p><ul>
<li><p>A <strong>Solana wallet</strong> (e.g. Phantom)</p></li>
<li><p>A small amount of <strong>SOL</strong> for fees</p></li>
<li><p>Some <strong>ATLAS</strong> to buy a starter ship, crew, and R4 resources</p></li>
</ul></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

